cpu_buf_vm_clear static key is only used by the MMIO Stale Data mitigation.
Rename it to avoid mixing it up with X86_FEATURE_CLEAR_CPU_BUF_VM.

Signed-off-by: Pawan Gupta <pawan.kumar.gupta@linux.intel.com>
